      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just not that simple. \"navigating a path forward\" sounds like something from a textbook, but there is no path. the debt is in the millions. the shame... it's like a physical weight in my chest. i look in the mirror and i don't even see a person anymore, just a massive mistake. everything i worked for is a lie. i just feel like there's no way to ever make this right or fix the damage i've caused. it feels like the only way to stop the feeling is to just... stop.",
